### =========================
### CLIENT FLOW
### =========================

### Register a new client
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clients/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "{{document}}",
  "name": "{{name}}",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "phone": "{{phone}}"
}

### Recharge wallet
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/recharge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "{{document}}",
  "phone": "{{phone}}",
  "amount": 1500
}

### Check balance
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/balance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "{{document}}",
  "phone": "{{phone}}"
}

### =========================
### PAYMENT FLOW (OTP)
### =========================

### Request payment (generates OTP and sends to email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "{{document}}",
  "phone": "{{phone}}",
  "amount": 50
}

### Confirm payment with OTP (edita @sessionId y @token arriba)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "token": "{{token}}"
}

### Get payment session status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/session/{{sessionId}}